    "page_richtext_section_47Vmda": {
      "type": "page-richtext-section",
      "blocks": {
        "richtext_787ewE": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "richtext": "<p>Some crystals should never be used when making crystal elixirs, massage oils or anything else you are consuming. Some are completely toxic or become toxic over time and others may be harmful to those with already existing illnesses, such as metal poisoning. Don’t be afraid or nervous to get in contact with me or anyone at Shiny Storm on this: <br/></p><h5>we are experts in deciphering which crystals will best help you on your journey to health, self-love and happiness.</h5><p>However, as a general rule, it is always best to use crystals indirectly, do not ingest your crystals.</p><p>*We will be writing more about toxic crystals and their safe uses soon*</p>",
            "cta_url": "",
            "cta_text": ""
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "richtext_787ewE"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "title-t": "",
        "title": "⇾ Crystals which may be harmful with direct use",
        "cta_url": "",
